<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Difference between ACCEL POS #1 and ACCEL POS #2 is greater than 0.02 V</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Difference between ACCEL POS #1 and ACCEL POS #2 is greater than 0.02 V</ptxt>
</entry>
